    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This driver-focused example retains its mechanical soul, featuring a robust powertrain with excellent compression across all cylinders. The naturally aspirated longitudinal engine delivers linear power through a crisp-shifting manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. It benefits from a recently refreshed suspension geometry, including high-durometer bushings and adjustable dampers that mitigate body roll while maintaining chassis composure. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the undercarriage is clean, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-capacity aluminum radiator. Recent service includes a full fluid flush (synthetic only) and a valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain remains quiet and efficient. Ready for the canyons or the track.",
