      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2019 Executive SUV in a striking Midnight Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been my daily driver and has never missed a scheduled service. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though I want to be transparent about a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium tan leather upholstery that remains supple and free of tears. All onboard technology\u2014including the 12.3-inch digital display, heated seats, and the premium surround-sound system\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; the turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming the brakes and suspension are in great shape. The tires are high-performance all-seasons with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle that offers luxury and reliability without the new-car price tag.",
